{
  "stem": "188.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 97.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I still fly off the handle when somebody else says, yes, but the Dutch were terrible, because [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to in one lifetime meet the kind of people that I've met is rather remarkable.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We tried to do some studying.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Which was-- we had no books, which was nearly impossible.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I read whatever was available.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were some old magazines, which, not speaking any English, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I picked out a word here and there, but those magazines, after a while, were no longer available.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They became toilet paper.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And magazine used extremely good paper.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, very smooth, very smooth.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] There was a supply of books, I guess the equivalent of Harlequin romances, that I, as an 11-year-old, read over and over and over, just to have something to do.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember birthdays were celebrated somehow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Even if it was just with an apple, it was-- it was recognized.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember one year getting three little tubes of water paint, and what a gift.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have not saved any of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't recall what I painted.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I just remember I got a yellow, a green, and a red tube of paint, and I thought this was-- this was heaven.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was the biggest gift.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Good.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Good.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was the only girl.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] The-- there were-- there was my brother, and there was another young boy, who was, I guess, one or two years younger than I was.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were three adults, my parents, my grandmother was there, my maternal grandmother, and three young men, Jewish young men, plus the sundry other people that were on the run that stopped in.",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
